25:26.680 --> 25:28.091
<i>"to read my book."</i>

25:28.240 --> 25:29.446
Augustus?

25:29.600 --> 25:30.761
<i>Yes?</i>

25:31.800 --> 25:32.801
What are you doing?

25:32.960 --> 25:33.961
<i>I may have found...</i>

25:34.040 --> 25:36.327
Van Houten's assistant,
emailed her.

25:36.400 --> 25:39.290
Augustus! She may have forwarded
that email on to Van Houten.

25:39.440 --> 25:40.441
<i>Shall I continue?</i>

25:40.640 --> 25:42.244
Oh, my God.
Yeah, go, go, go!

25:42.600 --> 25:44.728
"I am particularly
indebted to you, sir."

25:44.880 --> 25:47.645
Hazel Grace,
he just called me "sir."

25:47.800 --> 25:50.246
Augustus, keep reading,
keep reading!

25:50.600 --> 25:53.080
"Both for your kind words about
An Imperial Affliction...

25:53.280 --> 25:54.566
"and for taking the time...

25:54.720 --> 25:57.040
<i>"to tell me that the book, and
