26:00.160 --> 26:01.730
<i>(SHRIEKS) You did not!
You did not!</i>

26:01.880 --> 26:02.961
You did not, you did not!

26:03.160 --> 26:04.161
<i>Of course I did.</i>

26:04.240 --> 26:07.926
"To answer your question, no, I have
not written anything else, nor will I.

26:08.080 --> 26:10.242
<i>"I do not feel like continuing to
share my thoughts with readers...</i>

26:10.400 --> 26:11.680
<i>"would benefit
