26:11.760 --> 26:13.250
<i>"However, thank you...</i>

26:13.440 --> 26:14.646
"for your generous email.

26:14.840 --> 26:18.128
"Yours most sincerely,
Peter Van Houten."

26:20.160 --> 26:21.605
So, yeah, that just happened.

26:21.680 --> 26:22.681
(HAZEL EXHALES)

26:22.840 --> 26:24.251
Oh, my God.

26:24.400 --> 26:26.360
I've been trying to tell
you, I'm kind of awesome.

26:26.384 --> 26:27.431
(HAZEL LAUGHING)

26:28.280 --> 26:30.169
Do you think that I...

26:30.320 --> 26:31.401
Check your inbox.

26:31.680 --> 26:32.920
Oh, my God.

