27:48.080 --> 27:49.570
I think he'll like it.

27:55.440 --> 27:57.408
Is it really 1:00 AM?

27:57.520 --> 27:58.521
<i>Is it?</i>

27:58.600 --> 28:00.841
Yeah, I guess it is.
(HAZEL LAUGHS)

